n, often used as an\nexplosion proxy. Indeed, this ratio does tend to $\\sim1$ in conjunction with\nrunaway conditions, but neither this unit value nor the specific choice of the\ngain region as a point of reference appear to be distinct conditions in this\nregard.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Aug 2015 20:07:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-28"}
